function BookCreate() {
  return(<form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
      <label>Title:
      <input
        type='text'
        name='username'
        value={username}
        onChange={handleChange}/>
    </label>
    <label>Password:
      <input
        type='text'
        name='password'
        value={password}
        onChange={handleChange}/>
    </label>
    <button>Submit</button>
  </form>)
}
export default BookCreate
